'''Dhalbreth Square''' was an area on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. [[Jaina Solo Fel|Jaina Solo]] and [[Zekk]] were chased out of the square by [[New Republic Security Force]]s after they were caught swimming in a fountain that housed [[Glowfish/Legends|glowfish]].

